I89. Actions affecting property on which United States has lien

I11(a) Under the conditions prescribed in this section and section 1444 of this title for the protection of the United States, the United States may be named a party in any civil action or suit in any district court, or in any State court having jurisdiction of the subject matter_

I12(1) to quiet title to,

I12(2) to foreclose a mortgage or other lien upon,

I12(3) to partition,

